[info] DrawableComponentSpec:
[info] A DrawableComponent 
[info] - should have a well-defined starting Id
[info] - should preserves its id when casted down to MovableComponent
[info] - should change its (X,Y,Z) correctly
[info] - should change its (rotX, rotY, rotZ) correctly
[info] - should preserves its (X,Y,Z) when casted down to MovableComponent
[info] - should preserves its (rotX, rotY, rotZ) when casted down to MovableComponent
